reviews.review_data: Reviewed in the United States on October 18, 2020
reviews.name: Zachary P.
reviews.title: For the price it can't be beat
reviews.review: Your browser does not support HTML5 video. For what this CPU costs it's a steal for anyone looking to get into gaming and try out Ryzen.This runs on the Zen+ 2nd gen architecture (basically a 2600 but downclocked)If you're into content creation such as YouTube or any image editing, as well as gaming it's a good startup option for sure.if you only want to game a Ryzen 3 3300X is great too.But anyway this little guy runs all my games paired with a GTX 1060 6GB and 16GB of RAM with ease at high to max settings.Great power at a great price and that's pretty much all that needs to be said.Edit: it also seems amazon can't handle 1080p 60fps game clips Lol
